#' purposes.
#'
#' @format A data frame with 87 rows and 2 total columns. Columns Protein 1
#'     and Protein 2 are UniProt identifiers, and each row represents one
#'     pair of proteins with Uniprot Ids starting with the same 5 characters.
#'
#'
#' @examples
#' \dontrun{
#'  SARSCoV2Mapping
#' }
"SARSCoV2Mapping"

